data.description: What a view!  Perched above Skyline Parkway, this home offers views of Lake Superior.  You will find a nice sized living room with a gas fireplace and a dining room with a large window to enjoy the view. You will also find a cozy kitchen and bathroom. The two bedrooms offer hardwood floors.  The basement has the laundry, utilities, extra room for storage and access to the tuck-under garage. Located just over a mile up the 27th Ave W exit, you will have quick and easy access to the craft district, hiking trails, convenient shops and the highway without all the noise. Check out this charmer today and imagine the possibilities!
